PrecisAmendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (SCHEDULE NO. 1021) which sets a Maximum Residue Limit on the amount of "GLYPHOSATE" (a preplant or postharvest treatment used in the control of annual and perennial weeds on crop and noncrop land) that may be detected in oats.
